<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <title>Happy Birthday!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        margin: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        overflow: scroll;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        width: 40%;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
      .balloons {
        font-size: 4rem;
        animation: float 3s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
      }

      .card1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        height: 35rem;
        color: black;
      }
      @keyframes float {
        from {
          transform: translateY(70px);
        }
        to {
          transform: translateY(1rem);
        }
      }

      .cloud {
        background: white;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        width: 300px;
        height: 150px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #ff4081;
        box-shadow: 5px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      .cloud::before,
      .cloud::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 50%;
      }

      .cloud::before {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        top: -50px;
        left: 10px;
      }

      .cloud::after {
        width: 90px;
        height: 90px;
        top: -30px;
        right: 10px;
      }
      .btn{
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
        color: black;
        transform: translateX(-3.2rem);
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
      }

      @keyframes float {
        0% {
          transform: translateY(0rem);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-0.2rem);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateY(1rem);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="cloud">Happy Birthday Darpan!</div>
    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="balloons">🎈🎂🎉</div>
      <!-- <h1>Happy Birthday <b>Darpan</b >!</h1> -->
      <p class="card1">
        On this special day, I want to express how grateful
        I am to have you in my life. 💕 Your kindness and presence make every
        moment brighter! ✨ <br /><br />On your special day, I wish you wisdom
        🧠, success 🏆, and happiness 😊. May every decision you make lead you
        to greatness 🌟, and may you always find fulfillment in the beautiful
        journey of life. 🚀💫 A true friend like you is a gift. <br /><br />🎁💖
        Thank you for always being there, for your honesty, and for the
        countless moments of laughter 😂 and support 🤗. May this birthday bring
        you endless joy 🎊, success 💼, and all the happiness you deserve!
        Wishing you a fantastic day filled with love, laughter, and
        unforgettable memories! 🎈🥳💞
      </p>
    </div>
    <form action="/special" method="get">
    <div class="unknown">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary mt-5 offset-4">
          Why you are so special for me? Tap here to know
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
